Name: Symbiotic Love - Yuri Visual Novel
About the game: There's nothing new under the sun. All stories go like this: Encounter. Curiosity. Attraction. Love Two girls meet in a garden where the spider lilies bloom. One girl seeks the devil's gentleness. The other denies that the devil is capable of love at all. Will the spider lilies grow in a symbiotic relationship, or will they become like the higanbana, and part ways for good? Symbiotic Love is a coming-of-age Yuri Visual Novel set in an All Girls' High School, between two people fated to meet, become acquainted, friends, and eventually, lovers. Yet, what has fate in store for love so perfect, so symbiotic, that they could only live, and perish together? Features An emotional Yuri love story Full Mandarin voice acting Over 10+ Beautiful BGMs Over 10+ High-Resolution CGs Choice matters with different endings
